item.title: Superstar 360deg Shoes
item.dc:creator: lylephuong
item.description: Safer For The Environment: Our denim factory partner recycles 98% of their water using reverse osmosis filtration and keeps byproducts out of the environment by mixing them with concrete to create building materials.
item.content:encoded: Our favorite jean meets our favorite decade. Made from premium non-stretch Japanese denim for a vintage-inspired look, the ’90s Cheeky Jean has an easy straight leg, an extra-high rise, and a butt-boosting rear fit.
